page.title: 19TREE NURSERY
page.content: We did a project on trees and we found out there were not a lot of trees in Auchnagatt, so we decided to plant a few trees to liven up the Village. We planted a few different types of trees such as{Horse Chestnut,Broom, {Oak,Silver Birch,Weeping Beech,Rowan, {Elderberry,Elm Seeds,Alder. First of all we arranged to go to Aden park to collect seeds to plant in our Village. We left the seeds outside to break up(stratify). Then we planted them in the greenhouse to grow up,once they were at a certain lenth we dug them up and planted them in the tree nursery. We have planted{Elm}and{Broom} in our tree nursery and are going to plant acorns in a weeks time.We hope that in the future you will look back and see our trees that we have planted.
